Titolo: Creativerse

Anno: 2017

Descrizione: Creativerse is a free-to-play sandbox survival game developed by Playful Corp. for Microsoft Windows and macOS. Inspired by Minecraft, it takes place in a voxel-based world of blocks where players interact with flora and fauna, craft items, and build constructions. It first released as an early access title on Steam in August 2014 before officially releasing in May 2017.